ates the scalp to activate healthier hair growth<br\/><br\/>Rosemary extract boosts circulation around the follicles, encouraging stronger, fuller growth from the root.<\/p><p><br\/>Rebuilds weak, damaged strands with hydrolyzed keratin<br\/><br\/>Keratin peptides penetrate deeply to reinforce the hair shaft, reducing breakage and helping your hair grow longer without snapping.<br\/><\/p><p><br\/>Restores scalp balance for optimal growth conditions<br\/><br\/>Gently cleanses excess oil, product buildup, and dryness that can slow down healthy growth cycles.<br\/><\/p><p><br\/>Lightweight formula cleans effectively without stripping<br\/><br\/>Delivers nutrients without heaviness—leaving hair clean, soft, and ready to grow.<br\/><\/p><p><br\/>Strengthens hair to support long-term growth retention<br\/><br\/>With continued use, strands stay stronger, smoother, and more resilient, helping you finally keep the length you gain.<\/p>","question_4":"RADIANT ROOT RISK FREE GUARANTEE","answer_4":"<p>We want you to feel completely confident in your purchase.<\/p><p>That’s why every order is backed by our 60-day money-back guarantee.<\/p><p>If your item arrives damaged or defective, we’ll make it right with a replacement or full refund.<\/p><p>To start a return or exchange, simply contact our customer support team within 60 days of delivery. Share your order number and a quick description of the issue, and we’ll guide you through the process quickly and hassle-free.<\/p><p>Your satisfaction is our priority. We stand behind every product we make and are committed to delivering high-quality formulas and exceptional customer care.<\/p>","question_5":"","answer_5":"","question_6":"","answer_6":"","question_7":"","answer_7":"","question_8":"","answer_8":"","question_9":"","answer_9":"","question_10":"","answer_10":""}},"video_carousel_standalone_xw3T8p":{"type":"video_carousel_standalone","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"See it in action","heading_size":24,"heading_color":"#21